##spDataVersion:	1
##Title:	Montgomery New Testament
##Abbreviation:	MNT
##Information:	Montgomery New Testament (1924) by Helen Barrett Montgomery\par This is the only modem speech translation of the New Testament produced by a woman. Helen Barrett Montgomery's translation is marked by a conversational style, with the text arranged into paragraphs.
