B040C018V001	40	18	1	At that hour his disciples came to Jesus and asked him, "Who is really greatest in the kingdom of heaven?"
B040C018V002	40	18	2	When he had called a little child to him, Jesus set him among them,  and answered.
B040C018V003	40	18	3	"In solemn truth I tell you that unless you turn and become like little children, you will not even enter the kingdom of heaven.
B040C018V004	40	18	4	"Whoever therefore will humble himself like this little child, is greatest in the kingdom of heaven;
B040C018V005	40	18	5	"and whoever receives one such child for my sake, receives me.
