B040C018V015	40	18	15	"If your brother sins against you, go and show him, between yourself and him alone. If he listens, you have won your brother.
B040C018V016	40	18	16	"But if he will not listen to you, take one or two others along, so that by the testimony of two or three witnesses every word may be established. If he will not listen to them, tell the church;
