B041C008V011	41	8	11	And the Pharisees came out and began to question him, seeking from him a sign from heaven, by way of testing him.
B041C008V012	41	8	12	At this Jesus sighed deeply in his spirit, and said. "Why does the present generation seek a sign? In solemn truth I tell you that no sign shall be given this generation."
B041C008V013	41	8	13	Then he left them, and getting into the boat again, went away to the other side,
