B041C008V028	41	8	28	And they told him. "Some say Johnthe Baptist, others, Elijah, and others that you are one of the prophets."
B041C008V029	41	8	29	And he continued questioning them, "But you yourselves, Who do you say I am?" Peter in reply said to him, "You are Christ."
