B042C005V010	42	5	10	and so were Simons partners, Jamesand John, sons of Zebedee.) But Jesus answered Simon. "Fear not; from this time on, you will be catching men."
B042C005V011	42	5	11	So when they had brought their boats to land they left everything and followed him.
