B042C005V013	42	5	13	And he stretched out his hand and touching him, said. "I do choose;  be made clean."
B042C005V014	42	5	14	And instantly the leprosy left him. Jesus ordered him to tell no one, "But be off," he said, "show yourself to the priest, and make the offering for your cleansing, as Moses commanded, for a testimony to them."
