B042C005V022	42	5	22	Conscious of their cavilings, Jesus answered, saying.
B042C005V023	42	5	23	"What is this caviling in your hearts? Which is easier to say, "Your sins are forgiven," or to say, "Rise and walk?"
B042C005V024	42	5	24	But that you may know that the Son of man has authority on earth to forgive sins (he said to the paralytic), "I bid you rise, take up your bed, and go to your house."
B042C005V025	42	5	25	And instantly he arose up before them, took up what he had been lying on, and went away to his house, glorifying God.
