B042C005V039	42	5	39	"And no man after drinking old wine, wishes for new; for he says,  "The old is better.""
B042C006V001	42	6	1	It happened that on a Sabbath he was going through the wheat-fields.  His disciples were picking the ears and eating the wheat, rubbing it out with their hands.
