B044C002V042	44	2	42	and they stedfastly continued in the teaching of the apostles, and in the fellowship, in the breaking of the bread, and in the prayers.
B044C002V043	44	2	43	And awe came upon every soul, and many wonders and signs were wrought by the apostles.
B044C002V044	44	2	44	And all the believers were together, and had all things in common.
B044C002V045	44	2	45	They would sell their lands and other property, and distribute the proceeds among all, just as any one from time had need.
