B044C009V037	44	9	37	She, as it happened, was taken ill just at that time, and died.  After washing her body, they laid it in an upper room.
B044C009V038	44	9	38	And as Lydda was near Joppa, the disciples, when they heard that Peter was there, sent two men to him with the entreaty, "Delay not to come to us."
B044C009V039	44	9	39	So Peter arose and went with them. On his arrival they took him up-  stairs, and all the widows stood near him, weeping, and showing him the cloaks and garments which Dorcas used to make, while she was still with them.
B044C009V040	44	9	40	But Peter put them all out, and kneeled down, and prayed; and then turning to the body, he said, "Tabitha, rise!" She opened her eyes,  and on seeing Peter she sat up.
B044C009V041	44	9	41	Then he gave her his hand and raised her up, and after calling the saints and the widows, he gave her back to them alive.
