B066C007V006	66	7	6	Of the tribe of Asher, twelve thousand; Of the tribe of Naphtali,  twelve thousand; Of the tribe of Manasseh, twelve thousand;
B066C007V007	66	7	7	Of the tribe of Symeon, twelve thousand; Of the tribe of Levi,  twelve thousand; Of the tribe of Issachar, twelve thousand;
B066C007V008	66	7	8	Of the tribe of Zebulun, twelve thousand; Of the tribe of Joseph,  twelve thousand; Of the tribe of Benjamin, twelve thousand;
B066C007V009	66	7	9	After this I looked, and behold a great multitude, whom no man could number, out of every nation and tribe and people and tongue, standing before the throne and before the Lamb, clothed in white robes, with palm branches in their hands;
B066C007V010	66	7	10	and they cried with a loud voice, saying "Salvation to our God, who sits on the throne, And to the Lamb!"
