B066C007V012	66	7	12	and crying, "Even so! The blessing and the glory and the wisdom And the thanksgiving and the honor and the power and the might Be to our God forever and ever. Amen."
B066C007V013	66	7	13	And one of the Elders spoke to me, saying. "Who are these, clad in white robes? Whence come they?"
B066C007V014	66	7	14	And I said to him, "You know, my Lord." And he said to me, "These are those who have come out of the great persecution, and have washed their robes and made them white in the blood of the Lamb.
