B066C007V017	66	7	17	For the Lamb in the midst of the throne Will shepherd them, And will lead them to fountains of living water; And God will wipe away every tear from their eyes."
B066C008V001	66	8	1	And when he opened the seventh seal, there followed a silence in heaven, about the space of half an hour.
