B066C019V014	66	19	14	And the armies of heaven followed him upon white horses, clothed in fine linen, white and pure.
B066C019V015	66	19	15	And there issues from his lips a sharp sword with which to smite the nations. He shall shepherd them with a rod of iron. And he treads the winepress of the passion of the anger of Almighty God.
