B066C021V012	66	21	12	with a wall great and high, and twelve gates, and at the gates twelve angels; and names written thereon, the names of the twelve tribes of the children of Israel.
B066C021V013	66	21	13	On the east were three gates; and on the north, three gates; and on the south, three gates; and on the west, three gates.
B066C021V014	66	21	14	And the wall of the city had twelve foundations, and on them were the twelve names of the twelve apostles of the Lamb.
B066C021V015	66	21	15	And he who spoke had a golden reed, as a measure, to measure the city and its gates and walls.
B066C021V016	66	21	16	And the city lies foursquare; the length of it is as great as the breadth. Then he measured the city with the reed, fifteen hundred miles; the length and the breadth and the height of it are equal.
B066C021V017	66	21	17	And he measured its wall, two hundred and sixteen feet, mans measure, which is an angels.
B066C021V018	66	21	18	And its wall is made of jasper; but the city is of pure gold, like pure glass.
B066C021V019	66	21	19	The foundations of the wall of the city were adorned with all kings of precious stones. The first foundation-stone was jasper, the second sapphire, the third chalcedony, the fourth emerald,
B066C021V020	66	21	20	the fifth sardonyx, the sixth sardius, the seventh chrysolite, the eighth beryl, the ninth topaz, the tenth chrysoprase, the eleventh jacinth, the twelfth amethyst.
B066C021V021	66	21	21	And the twelve gates were twelve pearls; each gate of one pearl. And the broad street of the city was of pure gold, transparent like glass.
B066C021V022	66	21	22	And I saw no temple in the city; For the temple is the Lord God, the Almighty, And the Lamb.
B066C021V023	66	21	23	And the city has no need of the sun, Nor of the moon, to shine upon it; For the glory of God has lightened it, And its lamp is the Lamb.
B066C021V024	66	21	24	And the nations will walk by its light. And into it the kings of the earth will bring their glory;
B066C021V025	66	21	25	And its gates will not be shut by day, (For there is no night there);
B066C021V026	66	21	26	And they will bring the glory and honor Of the nations into it.
