B066C022V001	66	22	1	And he showed me the river of the Water of Life, clear as crystal,  Flowing out from the throne of God, and of the Lamb,
B066C022V002	66	22	2	In the middle of the broad street of the City. On each side of the river was a Tree of Life, Bearing twelve kinds of fruit, Each month yielding its own fruit. And the leaves of the tree Were for the healing of the nations.
