B066C022V006	66	22	6	Then he said to me. "These words may be trusted, and are true. the Lord, the God of the spirits of the prophets, has sent his angel to show his slaves what must soon take place.
B066C022V007	66	22	7	"And behold, I am coming quickly. Blessed is he who keeps the words of the prophecy of this book."
B066C022V008	66	22	8	And I, John, am he who heard and saw these things. And after I heard and saw them, I fell down to worship at the feet of the angel who showed them to me.
B066C022V009	66	22	9	But he said to me. "See thou do it not. I am only a fellow slave with you and your brothers, the prophets, and with those who keep the words of this Book. "WORSHIP GOD!"
B066C022V010	66	22	10	And he said to me, "Do not seal up the words of the prophecy of this book; for the crisis is near.
