B066C022V012	66	22	12	Behold, I come quickly; and my reward is with me, To give to each man what his actions merit.
B066C022V013	66	22	13	I am the Alpha and the Omega, The First and the Last, The Beginning and the End.
B066C022V014	66	22	14	"Blessed are they who wash their robes, so that they may have right to the Tree of Life, and may enter in by the gates into the City.
B066C022V015	66	22	15	Without are the dogs, the sorcerers, the immoral, the murderers, the idolaters, and all who live and make a lie.
B066C022V016	66	22	16	"I, Jesus, have sent my angel to give you this testimony for the churches. I am the root and offspring of David, the bright and morning Star.
B066C022V017	66	22	17	"And the Spirit and the Bride say Come! And let him who hears, say Come! And let him who thirsts, come; And whoever wills, let him take the Water of Life freely."
B066C022V018	66	22	18	I testify to every man who hears the words of the prophecy of this book. If any man shall add to them, God will add to him the plagues which are written in this book;
B066C022V019	66	22	19	and if any man shall take away from the words of the book of this prophecy, God will take away his share in the Tree of Life, and in the Holy City, about which this book is written.
B066C022V020	66	22	20	He who testifies this says, "Yea, I am coming quickly." Amen! Come,  Lord Jesus!
